{c={"* 30.17S, 54.71W - This is the entrance to the Barrow Downs.\n* 35.15S, 55.14W - Haudh Iarchith","You must be at least level 38 to start this deed"},d="Among the rotting horrors of the Barrow-downs, a gathering of corrupt and evil creatures holds sway over a black court. You must find and slay each of these evil abominations if there is to be any hope of wresting the grip of darkness from this once-hallowed place.",id=329,level=15,name="Executioner of the Wicked (Bree-land)",o="Defeat Brishzel in the barrow of Haudh Nogbenn (1)\nDefeat Umnen in the barrow of Ringdor (1)\nDefeat Fergandir in the barrow of Haudh Iarchith (1)\nDefeat Faegfaer in the barrow of Goetham (1)\nDefeat Marrow in the barrow of Haudh Methernil (1)\nDefeat Gwigon in the barrow of Taradan (1)",reputation={{val="+900 with Men of Bree"}},t="Slayer",titles={{val="Executioner of the Wicked"}},zone="Bree-land"},
