{d="The ruins of Minas Elendúr in Eregion and their under-cellars of Delotham have gone unexplored for long years since they were abandoned.",id=335,level=60,name="Exploration from Top to Bottom",o="Complete Chapter 6: Fúni Gem-cutter (1)\nFind Find the statue in the courtyard of Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the south-west corner of Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the enclosed porch in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the circular courtyard in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the south-east corner in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the south-east aisle in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the isolated chamber in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the dimly-lit, pillared room in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the windowed chamber in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the room of doors in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the room of dread in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the northern room in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the large balcony in Minas Elendúr\nFind Find the south-west corner of Delotham\nFind Find the illuminated room in Delotham\nFind Find the rubble-filled room in Delotham\nFind Find the buried room in Delotham\nFind Find the four-corridor junction in Delotham\nFind Find the illuminated bend in Delotham\nFind Find the central chamber in Delotham\nFind Find the collapsed corner in Delotham\nFind Find the sunken chamber in Delotham\nFind Find the northern chamber in Delotham",t="Explorer",titles={{val="the Thorough"}}},
