{d="Only by completing the tasks assigned to you by Uglash can you earn the favour of War-tyrant Akúlhun.",id=423,level=60,name="Gift from the War-tyrant",o="Report to Dâr-gazag, Maggot (1)\nInto the Grimwood (1)\nGet to Grothum, Maggot (1)\nReport to Lugazag (1)\nTo Tirith Rhaw (1)\nTo Tol Ascarnen (1)",receive={{id=70008841,val="Map to Gramsfoot"}},t="Reputation",titles={{val="Servant of Angmar"}}},
{c={"The following places are great to find Globsnaga Orcs:\n* North-west from The Chamber of Dark Waters at [16.9S, 111.9W] in The Water-works.\n* Dalgum-ru at [14.2S, 101.6W], south-west corner of The Foundations of Stone."},d="You have defeated a great number of the Globsnaga, the fungus-infested Orcs of Moria, and still you remain standing, having resisted the disease that wreaths these foes. They must be destroyed to the last, for the plague they bear is a perilous invention of the Enemy.",id=424,level=50,name="Globsnaga-slayer (Advanced) (Moria)",o="Defeat Globsnaga in Moria (240)",pois={{locations={"14.2S, 101.6W"},name="The Water-works",zone="Foundations of Stone"}},prev={425},reputation={{val="+700 with Iron Garrison Guards"}},t="Slayer",virtues={{val="Compassion"}},zone="Moria"},
{c={"The following places are great to find Globsnaga Orcs:\n* North-west from The Chamber of Dark Waters at [16.9S, 111.9W] in The Water-works.\n* Dalgum-ru at [14.2S, 101.6W], south-west corner of The Foundations of Stone."},d="Orcs infest the long, winding passages of Khazad-dûm, but a greater threat has arisen: the Globsnaga, Orcs infested by a vile fungus.",id=425,level=50,name="Globsnaga-slayer (Moria)",["next"]={424},o="Defeat Globsnaga in Moria (120)",pois={{locations={"14.2S, 101.6W"},name="The Water-works",zone="Foundations of Stone"}},reputation={{val="+700 with Iron Garrison Guards"}},t="Slayer",titles={{val="Bane of the Infected"}},zone="Moria"},
{d="The minions of the Enemy train in the Sword-hall of Dol Guldur, improving their skills for the inevitable invasion of Lothlórien. They must learn just how lacking they are....",id=426,level=60,name="Glory in the Sword-hall of Dol Guldur",o="Find\nComplete Enter the Arena (1)\nComplete Battle Royale (1)",receive={{id="7001F098",val="Malledhrim Gold Star Emblem"}},t="Lore",titles={{val="Victoriousthe Sword-halls"}}},
