{c={"Goblins can be found in the following places:\n* Tum Fuin\n* Tham Andalath"},d="The scourge of the goblins appears to be everywhere these days, even on the borders of the Shire itself. Rumour has it that in Evendim a new breed of the foul creatures can be found in the odd-looking Boggarts -- cowardly snivelling things that hunt in packs to bring down their prey.",id=436,level=23,name="Goblin-slayer (Evendim)",["next"]={430},o="Defeat goblins in Evendim (90)",t="Slayer",titles={{val="Goblin-foe"}},zone="Evendim"},
