{d="Goblins have made their home in Khazad-dûm like a swarm of ants, ever burrowing under the mountains and seeking the riches of the dwarves. To curb their growth would be a heroic deed, both in Moria and elsewhere in Middle-earth, for they are a dangerous nuisance wherever they reside.",id=438,level=50,name="Goblin-slayer (Moria)"},
