{d="Access to the depths of the Great Barrow and the gaunt-man Sambrog is gated by a key. One half lies within the maze, the other with Thadúr.",id=449,level=1,name="Great Barrow -- The Gate to Sambrog (Shadows of Angmar)",o="Defeat Thadúr the Ravager and claim half of the key (1)\nDefeat Gaerdring and Gaerthel and claim half of the key. (1)",receive={{id="700076BF",val="Skull Key"}},t="Slayer"},
