{c={"The following places are great to find gredbyg for this deed:\n* The Chittering Hole at [14.0S, 105.0W], south-west in The Redhorn Lodes.\n* The Palace of Náin at [6.6S, 113.6W], north from The Great Delving."},d="Now that some cleansing has been done against the vile insects of Moria, the effort must be ever maintained. Gredbyg do not ever truly leave a place, but their numbers should be quelled, lest the caves are overrun once more. To prevail against the gredbyg of Moria will be a tireless task.",id=458,level=50,mobs={{locations={"14.13S, 104.99W"},name="Grodbog Deep-queen",zone="Redhorn Lodes"},{locations={"9.09S, 113.51W"},name="Grodbog Guard",zone="Great Delving"},{locations={"13.62S, 112.02W"},name="Grodbog Guard",zone="Water-works"},{locations={"14.13S, 104.99W"},name="Grodbog Labourer",zone="Redhorn Lodes"},{locations={"9.09S, 113.51W"},name="Grodbog Labourer",zone="Great Delving"},{locations={"13.62S, 112.02W"},name="Grodbog Labourer",zone="Water-works"},{locations={"13.62S, 112.02W"},name="Grodbog Mantis",zone="Water-works"},{locations={"9.09S, 113.51W"},name="Grodbog Mantis",zone="Great Delving"},{locations={"9.09S, 113.51W"},name="Grodbog Queen",zone="Great Delving"},{locations={"13.62S, 112.02W"},name="Grodbog Queen",zone="Water-works"},{locations={"14.13S, 104.99W"},name="Grodbog Warrior",zone="Redhorn Lodes"}},name="Grodbog-slayer (Advanced) (Moria)",o="Defeat gredbyg in Moria (240)",pois={{locations={"14.0S, 105.0W"},name="The Chittering Hole",zone="Redhorn Lodes"},{locations={"6.6S, 113.6W"},name="The Palace of Náin",zone="Great Delving"}},prev={459},reputation={{val="+700 with Iron Garrison Guards"}},t="Slayer",virtues={{val="Discipline"}},zone="Moria"},
