{c={"Limrafn can be found throughout the Barandalf and Men Erain areas. Limrafn only come out at night."},d="You have seen many of these strange lights in Evendim lately -- they seem almost to be multiplying with the presence of Men and other forces. Is it possible that these strange entities are being awakened or attracted by the skirmishes being fought in this land, which was once nearly desolate and empty?",id=609,level=26,name="Limrafn-slayer (Advanced) (Evendim)",o="Defeat Limrafn in Evendim (240)",prev={610},t="Slayer",virtues={{val="Mercy"}},zone="Evendim"},
