{c={"The best place to find Nameless in Moria is the eastern part of The Foundations of Stone."},d="The Nameless seem to be corrupted creatures of an earlier age, though from what source their corruption comes or what they once were, none can say. They are deadly foes and attack without discrimination, hungry for the blood of any that wander too near their grasp.",id=698,level=53,mobs={{locations={"4.30S, 108.56W"},name="Grawulun the Caerog",zone="Durin's Way"}},name="Nameless-slayer (Moria)",["next"]={696},o="Defeat Nameless in Moria (120)",reputation={{val="+700 with Iron Garrison Guards"}},t="Slayer",titles={{val="Vanquisher of the Nameless"}},zone="Moria"},
