{c={"Sabre-tooth can be found in most areas on Forochel, scattered across the landscape. The best place to find them is:\n* Leijona-kotin\n* the path up Pynti-leiri"},d="The sabre-tooth cats are a deadly and frequent hazard of the forests of Forochel. Only the bravest hunters amongst the Lossoth will dare to hunt in the vicinity of a Sabertooth den, and even they occasionally fail to return.",id=808,level=40,name="Sabre-tooth Slayer (Advanced) (Forochel)",o="Defeat sabre-tooth in Forochel (300)",prev={809},t="Slayer",virtues={{val="Fortitude"}},zone="Forochel"},
{c={"Sabre-tooth can be found in most areas on Forochel, scattered across the landscape. The best place to find them is:\n* Leijona-kotin\n* the path up Pynti-leiri"},d="These savage cats are predators of a particularly vicious and undiscerning nature. The Lossoth make sure to respect their territory during the hunt, lest they become a meal for these deadly creatures. Likewise what livestock they raise is under constant threat by these voracious beasts.",id=809,level=40,name="Sabre-tooth Slayer (Forochel)",["next"]={808},o="Defeat sabre-tooths in Forochel (150)",t="Slayer",titles={{val="Fang-breaker"}},zone="Forochel"},
{c={"The island Tyl Ruinen west of Tinnudir, is the best place to find salamanders."},d="Oddly, Salamanders are frequently found near bodies of water such as rivers or lakes -- though they may also be found in wet marshes or sandy deserts. Scholars believe this may be because of the creature's tendency to burn away all nearby vegetation, thus rendering an area uninhabitable unless bodies of water or otherwise fire-proof terrain serves to constrain the fires they so freqently set.",id=810,level=26,name="Salamander-slayer (Advanced) (Evendim)",o="Defeat Salamanders in Evendim (240)",prev={811},t="Slayer",virtues={{val="Determination"}},zone="Evendim"},
{c={"The island Tyl Ruinen west of Tinnudir, is the best place to find salamanders."},d="The Salamanders of Evendim have always been a rare sight. This odd offshoot of the family of dragons has a strong affinity for fire, which it wields with abandon against any enemy that disturbs it.",id=811,level=26,name="Salamander-slayer (Evendim)",["next"]={810},o="Defeat Salamanders in Evendim (120)",t="Slayer",titles={{val="Quencher of Flames"}},zone="Evendim"},
